  "title": "Uploading a Single File (/sdks/(clis)/ardrive-cli/(working-with-files)/uploading-a-single-file)",
  "content": "To upload a file, you'll need a parent folder id, the file to upload's file path, and the path to your wallet:\n\nNOTE: To upload to the root of a drive, specify its root folder ID as the parent folder ID for the upload destination. You can retrieve it like so:",
